  "body": "### Component\n\nForge\n\n### Describe the feature you would like\n\n# Motivation \r\nI want to auto-generate re-mappings  \r\nAlso Im lazy, so I do in existing repo\r\n\r\n```sh\r\n# in an existing repo \r\nforge config --basic > foundry.toml\r\n```\r\nI get\r\n\r\n```toml\r\n[default]\r\nsrc = 'contracts'\r\nout = 'out'\r\nlibs = ['lib']\r\nremappings = [\r\n    'ds-test/=lib/ds-test/src/',\r\n    'solmate/=lib/solmate/src/',\r\n    'weird-erc20/=lib/solmate/lib/weird-erc20/src/',\r\n]\r\n```\r\n\r\n## possible aliases \r\n\r\n```sh\r\n$ forge bootstrap\r\n$ forge laforge\r\n$ forge config init\r\n$ forge r\r\n```\r\n\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_",
